<em>lasmotherium haimatos</em>, the Blood Unicorn.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"mar=
gin: 16px 0;">Now of course it is 2022 and we are all a bit more jaded. The=
re was the SoftBank boom, we=E2=80=99ve had a couple of years of SPACs, the=
re is so much crypto. Raising hundreds of millions of dollars from gullible=
 investors who don=E2=80=99t do much due diligence is not particularly impr=
essive anymore. If you want to do it by pretending to have a technology, yo=
u can (try <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/2625347=
5.277659/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMD=
