al. =E2=80=9CIn the past year, there has been a notable rush of funding int=
o the high-risk category of early-stage startups, as investors have clamore=
d to get into companies even before they had a staff or product,=E2=80=9D t=
he Wall Street Journal <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/c=
